
Ham and Potato Soup


1 package scalloped potatoes – plus ingredients as package directs
½ bag frozen broccoli cuts
½ pound cooked ham cut into ½ inch cubes
½ cup shredded cheddar cheese (optional)
½ cup milk
½ cup water
Prepare potatoes according to package directions for stove method, 
adding broccoli and ham when adding milk and butter.  
Add milk and water.  Stir in cheese just before serving.Makes 4 servings
